10 An Act relating to higher education; prohibiting
certain institutions of higher education from using
11 state funds, property, or resources to support or
require certain activities related to diversity,
12 equity, and inclusion; requiring certain institutions
of higher education to initiate certain review after
13 certain date; providing for restructuring or
elimination of certain unnecessary functions;
14 providing certain construction; requiring certain
institutions to submit certain annual certificate of
15 compliance by certain date; providing for
promulgation of rules; providing for codification;
16 providing an effective date; and declaring an
emergency.
17
18
19 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
20 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
21 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 3251 of Title 70, unless there
22 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
